  m_Name: Ocean Sprit Revenge
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  encounterName: Ocean Spirit Revenge
  text: The clouds block out the sun with supernatural speed. The world darkens around
    you and the wind disappears from your sails. For what feels like forever, the
    ocean around you is utterly silent and still. You hold your breath. Suddenly,
    the water erupts from all sides of the ship and the three ocean spirits from
    before bear their watery fangs and come crashing down upon the ship...
